root header recipient broker brokerRegisterNo
Type: string

Register number of the broker. Register number for the independent intermediaries as defined by the IG B2B ; prefix with country code and register plus register number FINMA or FMA (example: CHE-FINMA-10001). Note for insurers: For those intermediaries who are not at FINMA or FMA but want to participate on electronic data exchange, e.g., in-house brokers, the code assigned by IG B2B (example: CHE-IGB2B-50001) must be recorded.

 Must match regular expression: ^(CHE\-(FINMA\-(\d{5}|\S{9})|IGB\dB\-(\d{5}))|LIE\-FMA\-\S{5})$
